peopleAlsoAsk.question: How do I know if my bicentennial quarter is rare?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet:
How can you tell if a bicentennial quarter is rare? Firstly, take note of the condition of the coin. Coins that are in mint or near-mint condition typically hold greater value than those that show signs of wear and tear. Look for any scratches, discoloration, or other damages that may affect its worth.
